title: Aye Hamare Baap
content:
1 - Aye Hamare Baap

Chorus:
Aye Hamare Baap
To Joh Aasman Mein Hei
Tera Naam Paak Mana Jaye
Teri Baadshahat Ho.
-Aye…
Jaise Ki Teri Marji
Aasmaan Mein Puri Hoti
Vaise Hi Teri Marji
Jamin Par Puri Ho Jave.

Rooz Ki Roti Hamari Aaaj Stu Humko De De
Jeevan Ki Roti Tu Hai To Hi Hamara Bal Hai.

Jis Tarah To Apne Apradh Ko Maaf Karta
Usi Tarah To Hamare Apradh Ko Maaf Kar De.

title: Stuthi Aradhana Upar Jaati Hai
content:
2 - Stuthi Aradhana Upar Jaati Hai

Stuthi Aradhana Upar Jaati Hai
Aashish Lekar Niche Aati Hai(2)

Dekho Humse Karta Hai Pyaar(2)

Ha-A-Le-Lu Ha-Le-Lu-U-Yah(2)

Prarthana Bindhi Upar Gaati Hai
Uthar Lekar Niche Aati Hai(2)

title: Aaya Masih Duniya Mein To
content:
3 - Aaya Masih Duniya Mein To

Chorus:
Aaya Masih Duniya Mein To
Papiyo Ko Bachane Ko
Laye Ye Maan Jo Bête Par
Karege Par Yis Duniya Ko.

Duniya Gunah Mein Doob Rahi Thi
Sare Gumrah Ho Rahe The
Choda Aasmaan, Bana Insaan
Mili Najaat Is Duniyah Ko.(2)

Samuda Ki Sab Lehron Par
Duniya Ki Har Jubano Par
Hai Uska Naam, Hai Uska Kaam
Sara Jahan Laye Inaam(2)

title: Dheemi Ek Dheemi
content:
4 - Dheemi Ek Dheemi

Dheemi Ek Dheemi
Awaz Aa Rahi Hain
Suli Se Suli Se Suli Se.

Gum Se Bhari Aasu Tale
Jeevan Lagi Besahara(2)
Paas Aao Mein Tumhe Shanti Aaram
Deta Hun(2) -Dheemi…

Dukhi Toh Takh Bhi Gaye
Ghabra Gaye Zindagi Se
Paas Aao Mein Tumhe Ek Naya Mann
Deta Hun(2) -Dheemi…

title: Geet tere hum gayen
content:
5 - Geet tere hum gayen

Geet tere hum gayen

Bin baha kar gayen Stuti karte aaye

To hi hamara taran hara

Pyar tera hi payen

Swarg choda duniya mein aaya

Paapon ko mere june uthaya

Sooli pe tune khoon bahaya

Khoon bahaya mujhko bachaya

Paapon mein dooba manush hai bechara
Dhundtha phirtha hai who kinara
Dekh saka na tu ye nazara
Ban ilya tu uska sahara
Accha sahara, sabka sahara

title: Aawaz ultayenge hum saaz bajayenge
content:
6 - Aawaz ultayenge hum saaz bajayenge

Aawaz ultayenge hum saaz bajayenge

Heh Yesu mahan apna

Yeh geet sunayenge – Aawaz

Sansar ke sundarathame Yeh reputho tera hee

In chand si taro may – aksath tho tera hee

Mahima kee there bathe – hum sabko bathayenge

Heh Yesu mahan apna – Yeh geet sunayenge

Dil tera khajana he – ek paak muhabath ka
Ye paa na saka koyee saagar hibthu ulath ka
Ham teri muhabbath se – dil apna saja yenge
He Yesu mahan apna – Yeh geet sunayenge

title: Param Pita ki hum stuti gayen
content:
7 - Param Pita ki hum stuti gayen

Param Pita ki hum stuti gayen
Woh hi hai jo bachatah hamen
Sare paapon ko karta kshama
Sare rogom ko karta change

1. Dhanyawad de uske asanoa mein
Anand se aye uske charano mein
Sangit gaakar khushi se
Mukti ke chattanko jay lalkarey

2. Who hi hamara hai param Pita
Taras khata hai sarva sada
Purab se paschhim hai jitni door
Utari hi door kiye hamare gunah

title: Har dil mei hai Prabuji
content:
8 - Har dil mei hai Prabuji

Har dil mei hai Prabuji

Har sason me hai Prabhuji

Dukh me bhi hai Prabhuji

Har kushi me hai prabhuji

Phir tumhara man kyon ghabraye

Jab paas ho Prabhu tumhare

1. Zindegi ke is safar mein
Khona bhi hai paana bhi hai
Rona bhi hai aur hasna bhi hai
Tay karna hai yeh safar to yesu
Ke sang tum chalo

2. Zindegi ka hai samay kam
Lamba hai safar pathreeli dagar
Andheyaari si raat me hai jana kahan
Mein rahi hoo akela Prabhuji manjil hai

title: Kya tum zindagi se thake huye ha (Give them all)
content:
9 - Kya tum zindagi se thake huye ha (Give them all)

Kya tum zindagi se thake huye ha
Kya tum zindagi se bhatak rahe ho
Chur hoye sapno se tum bahaar niklo
Yeshu ke charan par rakh dho

Chorus:
De doh sab De doh sab
De doh sab kuch Yeshu ko
Unke sapne zakhmi dil bigadya ga
De doh sab De doh sab
De doh sab kuch Yeshu ko
Who hi saare dukhon ko
Sukhi mein badal ye ga

Usne hahi kaha such na hoga
Usne nahi kaha dukh na hoga
Wada kiya tha geet bhara dil
Zindagi ki geet gathe chal

title: Dekho dekho kaun aa raha, jalai yeshu raja
content:
10 - Dekho dekho kaun aa raha, jalai yeshu raja

Dekho dekho kaun aa raha, jalai yeshu raja
Nazrre uthakar dekhlo, yeh kaisa shahansha hai

Dulhan ko sath lene, akshay jeevan dene
Swargiya sena sang who aa raha hai (2)

(Dekho dekho…)

Duto ka lalkar sunai dega

Parmeshwar ke turhi funki jayegi (2)

Hosanna hosanna (4)
Duto ka lalkar…

Masih mere, ji uthenge,
aur jeevitho ke sang aa Milenge

Anokha hai rupanthar,
pal bhar main hai arohan

Hoga hamara Milan dulhe ke sath

(dekho dekho… Raha hai)

(dekho dekho… Shahansha hai)

Sare dukh hamara bhula dega who
Sare aankoh se aansu yeshu pochega (2)
Hosanna hosanna (4)
Sare dukh…
Pahanayaga, jalali sehra, dega hame anant mahima
Jay jay ho yeshu ki, hallelujah ke geet
Sada wahan, parhum, gaate rahenge

(dekho dekho… Raha hai)
(dekho dekho… Shahansha hai)
